00:41:05.050 --> 00:41:09.580
because if we take the
integral of mu times N2--

00:41:09.580 --> 00:41:11.080
let's see.

00:41:11.080 --> 00:41:12.700
Oh, yeah, this is right.

00:41:12.700 --> 00:41:22.960
So we have lambda plus
