00:41:45.250 --> 00:41:51.895
So we can say, N2
times mu prime--

00:41:54.780 --> 00:42:03.530
let's see-- equals mu sigma-59
phi e to the minus sigma

00:42:03.530 --> 00:42:08.730
59 phi times t.

